 CellLabel->"In[63]:=",ExpressionUUID->"d761ca10-8b03-4352-8156-4151362333d1"],

Cell["\<\
The following rule allow to pass from \[Psi]\[CloseCurlyQuote] to X and vice \
versa. Also, Xe[r]=X, it is just another notation that keeps track of the \
dependency of X on r.\
\>", "Text",
